      public void timeoutAsync(long now)
      Check to see if the timeout has expired and process a timeout if that is the case. Note: The name of this method originated with the Servlet 3.0 asynchronous processing but evolved over time to represent a timeout that is triggered independently of the socket read/write timeouts.
